    <h1>Epic Tetris Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: May 02, 2024</p>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>Epic Tetris collects and stores the following information locally on your device:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Game high scores</li>
            <li>Game preferences and settings</li>
            <li>Device information (device type, operating system)</li>
            <li>Analytics data about game usage</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the collected information to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Save and display your high scores locally on your device</li>
            <li>Remember your game preferences and settings</li>
            <li>Provide technical support</li>
            <li>Analyze game usage patterns</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>3. Data Storage</h2>
        <p>Game data is stored locally on your device using Android SharedPreferences. This data remains on your device and is not transmitted to our servers. The data may be included in your device's backup if you have enabled Android backup services.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>4. Advertisements</h2>
        <p>Epic Tetris uses Google AdMob for displaying banner advertisements. Google AdMob may collect and use data to show relevant ads, including:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Device identifiers (Advertising ID)</li>
            <li>IP address</li>
            <li>General location (country/region)</li>
            <li>App usage data</li>
        </ul>
        <p>For more information about how Google uses data, please visit <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites">Google's Privacy & Terms</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>5. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>Epic Tetris does not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you are a parent and believe your child has provided personal information, please contact us.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>6. Changes to Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at:</p>
        <p>Email: contact.hrzn@gmail.com</p>
    </div>
